"--Quick Movements in Insert Monde--

noremap! <Leader>l <right>
noremap! <Leader>j <down>
noremap! <Leader>k <up>
noremap! <Leader>h <left>

"window and pane navigation
imap <C-h> <C-w>h
imap <C-j> <C-w>j
imap <C-k> <C-w>k
imap <C-l> <C-w>l
nnoremap <C-h> <C-w>h
nnoremap <C-j> <C-w>j
nnoremap <C-k> <C-w>k
nnoremap <C-l> <C-w>l

"for escape mode from insert mode
inoremap jk <Esc>
inoremap kj <Esc>
